p: The chemical composition of Compound Anshen essential oil was determined by gas chromatography-mass spectrometry (GC-MS). Searches through the PubChem (https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/), STITCH (http://stitch.embl.de/), and TCMSP (http://lsp.nwu.edu.cn/tcmsp.php) databases provided chemical composition targets.
